Name: Who Are You?
About the game: Who Are You? is an open world, narrative game set in limbo, moments after she has taken her own life. Walkthrough all of the key moments that had let her into taking her own life. But only after she travels through these moments for the second time in limbo she comes to the realization that she has made a mistake in doing so. KEY FEATURES *A compelling story that will pull on your heartstring and make you feel for the action of action she has taken. *A really beautiful-looking world with tons of amazing colors.
